### Positioning Statement

> OptX is an AI-powered business simulation platform that ingests a company's financial data, runs a 5-layer mathematical pipeline (Monte Carlo, Bayesian networks, sensitivity analysis, backtesting), and uses 6 specialized AI agents to generate actionable "what-if" scenarios — turning weeks of consulting work into minutes.

